    "Psge Four TOLEDO UNION JOURNAL Official Publication Toledo Industrial Union Council ORGANIZE TOLEDO 100 Published every Friday by Local No 12 UAWCIO 425 Winthrop Street Toledo Ohio of American Labor Pr Association Editor______ Melvin Schult Managing Editor O J Pocord Member American Newspaper GuildClO Advertising ManagerBurny Zawodny Board of Trustees Melvin Schults Thomas Burke Randolph Gray SUBSCRIPTION RATES Entered at the Toledo Ohio post office as One year by mail in advance 15t second class matter under the act of Aug 24 1912 Greofesf Crisis American labor today faces the great est crisis in its history Even the most casual reading of the TaftHartley bills or the Ohio Van Aken bill makes us want to pinch ourselves to see if we are awake They are like taking pages from Hitlers Mein Kampf No longer are we dealing with the theories of the alarmists who for years told us that it can happen here We face to face with deadly reality in the shape of legislation which if it is passed will find us but a short step away from Fascism and everything that goes with brutalitarian government Nor should we lull ourselves into a false sense of security by assuring"
